     "Of course." Myrmidon's voice was all business as
he turned in the direction of the signal. Although his
movements were purposeful and sure he wondered at the
newness of everything. He had no memories of anything
from before he 'woke up' but couldn't help but feel
that something is somehow different then the way its
'suppose' to be. When he thought this Hydras who was
some form of Megatron, but not the one he knew, there
was an odd feeling of both joy and tripidation. With a
quick shake of his head he thrust his feelings aside
as he moved towards Hydras' signal.

OOC: Is Myrmidon entering the base, or is he going
elsewhere?

Preston
(Myrmidon)
